    "description": "<div style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#222;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto\" vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n  <div style=\"display:none\"><span property=\"description\">Whether you&#039;re new to gold panning or are an experienced gold prospector, you know how important it is to be able to successfully and efficiently classify your raw material down to usable paydirt, either for panning or to run through a sluice box to find gold nuggets, gems or other. The ASR Outdoor collapsible bucket, collapsible stand and classifier screen does just this in just a few easy steps!</span></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px 15px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:6px\">Deals Only Web Store</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#333\">Our Store</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:22px;margin:0 0 12px\">ASR Outdoor Classifier Screen Set with 10L Collapsible Bucket Kit (4 Sizes)</h2>\n  <p>Whether you&#039;re new to gold panning or are an experienced gold prospector, you know how important it is to be able to successfully and efficiently classify your raw material down to usable paydirt, either for panning or to run through a sluice box to find gold nuggets, gems or other. The ASR Outdoor collapsible bucket, collapsible stand and classifier screen does just this in just a few easy steps!</p>\n  <p>The ASR Outdoor collapsible bucket has been designed to work seamlessly with the included ASR Outdoor sifting pan; together they make a an efficient classification system that is easy to set up and take down, lightweight and reliable. The collapsible bucket is a lightweight alternative to a traditional 5 gallon bucket, which can be heavy and cumbersome to use, as well as carry to and from your gold claim site. To use the bucket and stand combo, you simply slide the four arms into the base and rotate until they lock in place. Then place the collapsible bucket over the tops of the arms and secure. Next, add your sifter and you&#039;re ready to start classifying your raw material.</p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Key Features</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>10L COLLAPSIBLE BUCKET WITH STAND:</strong> Space saving, compact and an incredibly useful tool to include with your gold prospecting equipment; the collapsible bucket is a lightweight alternative to a traditional 5 gallon bucket, which can be heavy and cumbersome to carry to and from your gold claim site</li>\n    <li><strong>CLASSIFIER SCREEN:</strong> Included sifting pan classifier screen is used to efficiently classify raw material down to paydirt for further gold panning or to run through a sluice box; the collapsible stand is fast and easy to put together and sturdy enough to support the weight of several sifter screens up to 30lbs</li>\n    <li><strong>MESH BAG INCLUDED:</strong> A handy mesh bag is included to make carrying the collapsible bucket and stand components easier, while allowing for tidy and organized storage when you&#039;re not utilizing your gold prospecting equipment</li>\n    <li><strong>COLLAPSIBLE BUCKET FEATURES:</strong> The collapsible bucket is made from BPA free silicone, features a sturdy carrying handle, hang tab, bottom finger indentation and water pouring channel; the bucket can also be employed for tons of other uses outside of gold panning kits like fishing, gardening, as an ice bucket, for camping and much more</li>\n    <li><strong>SPECIFICATIONS:</strong> Open Dimensions: 12 x 10 inches; Collapsed Dimensions: 12 x 2 inches; Bucket Capacity: 10L or 2.64 Gallons; Color: Grey, Orange; Material: Plastic, Silicone; Weight: 2.3lbs; Note: Classifier screens are NOT included</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 16px\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/usurper-products/71717/1QoNKrova4oNBOKIuQcQVixovKBPk6-metaQmlrTnI2RWZZYTRMQ21TTGVEQjZxV1ZYSHhQQWkzLW1ldGFSMUEyTFVKVE5TMHhNRXhmWTI5c2JHRndjMmxpYkdWZlluVmphMlYwWDNOMFlXNWtYMk5zWVhOemFXWnBaWEpmYTJsMFh6QXpMbXB3Wnc9PS0uanBn-.jpg\" alt=\"Whether you&#039;re new to gold panning or are an experienced gold prospector, you know how important it is to be able to successfully and efficiently\" style=\"max-width:100%;width:600px;height:auto\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Product Specifications</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>MPN:</strong> L015SB6PGPARENT</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p>The classifier screen we&#039;ve included in this gold panning kit is made from high impact, durable ABS plastic and will stand up to lots of gold prospecting equipment wear and tear. This sifting screens will allow you to classify down material to usable paydirt, removing larger unwanted materials like rocks and gravels, leaving you with just sand, fine gravels and hopefully gold nuggets! And, as mentioned, the sifters are designed to be stacked on top of the collapsible bucket for quick and efficient processing of unclassified paydirt.</p>\n  <p>The collapsible bucket is made from BPA free silicone, features a sturdy carrying handle, bottom finger indentation and water pouring channel; the bucket can also be employed for tons of other uses outside of gold panning kits like fishing, gardening, as an ice bucket, for camping and much more. Lastly, a handy mesh bag is included to make carrying the collapsible bucket and stand components easier, while allowing for tidy and organized storage when you&#039;re not utilizing your gold prospecting equipment to ensure none of the pieces are lost (does not fit the classifier screen).</p>\n  <p>The collapsible bucket with stand is space saving, compact and lightweight in design, and overall a useful and versatile tool to include with your gold prospecting equipment.</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 0\"><img src=\"https://s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/DOWS_photobucket/Shopify_Prop65graphic.jpg\" alt=\"California Proposition 65 warning\" style=\"display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" height=\"78\" width=\"273\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:18px 0 0;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid #e5e5e5;font-size:13px;color:#777;text-align:center\">&copy; 2026 Deals Only Web Store</p>\n</div>",
    "short_description": "Whether you're new to gold panning or are an experienced gold prospector, you know how important it is to be able to successfully and efficiently classify your raw material down to usable paydirt, either for panning or to run through a sluice box to find gold nuggets, gems or other. The ASR Outdoor collapsible bucket, collapsible stand and classifier screen does just this in just a few easy steps!.",
